WEBVTT

1
00:00:10.728 --> 00:00:11.898
Ready?

2
00:00:12.567 --> 00:00:13.697
Action.

3
00:00:36.858 --> 00:00:38.587
Cut! Great job!

4
00:01:36.888 --> 00:01:37.888
(Song Geu Rim)

5
00:02:38.447 --> 00:02:39.778
Good work today.

6
00:03:06.678 --> 00:03:07.877
That hurts.

7
00:03:28.227 --> 00:03:29.498
What's wrong with you?

8
00:03:29.868 --> 00:03:31.368
Will taking you home do?

9
00:03:32.428 --> 00:03:34.768
The drama world is
repaying the drama world,

10
00:03:34.768 --> 00:03:36.097
so let's call it even.

11
00:03:36.338 --> 00:03:39.468
And don't follow me around
anymore.

12
00:03:39.577 --> 00:03:40.637
Okay?

13
00:03:41.338 --> 00:03:43.278
I'll never do radio.

14
00:03:44.148 --> 00:03:46.947
Forget it. I'll go alone
even if I have to crawl.

15
00:04:03.167 --> 00:04:05.667
Put me down!

16
00:04:08.438 --> 00:04:10.268
I said to put me down.

17
00:04:20.077 --> 00:04:22.817
Do you hate me that much?

18
00:04:23.017 --> 00:04:24.017
Why?

19
00:04:24.217 --> 00:04:27.158
Or do you hate the radio
that much? Why?

20
00:04:27.457 --> 00:04:29.288
What do you hate so much?

21
00:04:29.288 --> 00:04:31.587
Why must I tell you that?

22
00:04:36.098 --> 00:04:38.567
You tripped me on purpose
four years ago...

23
00:04:38.567 --> 00:04:40.567
at the charity ball,
didn't you?

24
00:04:40.868 --> 00:04:42.137
Do you think I'm stupid?

25
00:04:42.137 --> 00:04:43.868
You say things
to anger me...

26
00:04:43.868 --> 00:04:45.408
and start fights with me.

27
00:04:45.608 --> 00:04:48.007
What did I do to you?

28
00:04:48.007 --> 00:04:50.548
What's your problem?

29
00:05:13.967 --> 00:05:16.137
Where are we going?

30
00:05:16.938 --> 00:05:18.137
Let me off.

31
00:05:18.137 --> 00:05:20.038
I'm not going
to the hospital.

32
00:05:23.978 --> 00:05:26.248
How can you ignore me
at a time like this?

33
00:05:42.627 --> 00:05:43.627
Wait...

34
00:05:44.267 --> 00:05:46.467
How did you know
I live here?

35
00:05:47.197 --> 00:05:50.538
How did you know
I live here?

36
00:05:51.038 --> 00:05:53.808
- Get out.
- How did you know?

37
00:05:53.808 --> 00:05:55.178
Do you need me
to carry you out again?

38
00:05:56.577 --> 00:05:58.007
Are you not getting out...

39
00:05:58.007 --> 00:05:59.777
because you want me
to hold you again?

40
00:06:24.238 --> 00:06:25.337
Ji Soo Ho.

41
00:06:25.507 --> 00:06:28.308
You can't just disappear
from a shoot like that.

42
00:06:28.308 --> 00:06:29.777
What about your schedule?

43
00:06:30.408 --> 00:06:33.418
You have to tell me
if you're leaving.

44
00:06:33.418 --> 00:06:35.877
It doesn't matter if it's
2 minutes or 2 hours,

45
00:06:35.877 --> 00:06:37.488
you would be considered
missing to us.

46
00:06:49.058 --> 00:06:51.168
Did you drive
that girl home?

47
00:06:51.428 --> 00:06:52.668
You can go now.

48
00:06:54.038 --> 00:06:56.707
I took care of the
commercial shoot.

49
00:06:57.207 --> 00:06:59.108
You never acted
like this before...

50
00:06:59.577 --> 00:07:00.678
Mr. Kim.

51
00:07:01.108 --> 00:07:03.877
I told you that you can go
with a smile.

52
00:07:13.688 --> 00:07:15.618
- What is this?
- Open the door.

53
00:07:15.618 --> 00:07:16.627
(Visiting system,
I can hold my tongue)

54
00:07:16.627 --> 00:07:17.858
Ji Soo Ho.

55
00:07:19.558 --> 00:07:20.598
What is this?

56
00:07:20.757 --> 00:07:22.428
Do you have fans
stalking you?

57
00:07:22.798 --> 00:07:23.967
If you don't open up,

58
00:07:23.967 --> 00:07:26.197
I could make
a scene out here.

59
00:07:26.197 --> 00:07:27.798
Who is this guy?

60
00:07:28.598 --> 00:07:29.668
I'll get rid of him.

61
00:07:35.777 --> 00:07:36.877
I told you to go.

62
00:07:43.317 --> 00:07:44.447
Who are you?

63
00:07:46.788 --> 00:07:48.257
I'm Ji Soo Ho's manager.

64
00:07:50.387 --> 00:07:52.087
All right. Excuse me.

65
00:08:05.808 --> 00:08:07.308
Maybe
I should be your manager.

66
00:08:07.308 --> 00:08:08.837
Why do you have
so much stuff?

67
00:08:09.848 --> 00:08:11.048
I'm going to live here.

68
00:08:12.447 --> 00:08:13.447
I entered
medical school...

69
00:08:13.577 --> 00:08:15.947
as a top student and
graduated with top scores.

70
00:08:15.947 --> 00:08:17.387
Did you know that?

71
00:08:19.817 --> 00:08:21.188
You won't
get your treatment...

72
00:08:21.188 --> 00:08:23.058
nor come in
for consultation.

73
00:08:23.058 --> 00:08:24.827
You won't listen to me,
so...

74
00:08:24.827 --> 00:08:25.827
So?

75
00:08:27.197 --> 00:08:29.298
I will follow you around
24 hours a day.

76
00:08:29.868 --> 00:08:31.267
You're in for trouble.

77
00:08:31.827 --> 00:08:33.567
I'm hungry.
Do you have any food?

78
00:08:41.607 --> 00:08:43.077
That sounds like fun.

79
00:08:43.347 --> 00:08:45.648
Do I get to take writers
to hotels too?

80
00:08:47.977 --> 00:08:49.987
I never came here
with a writer before.

81
00:08:56.327 --> 00:08:58.388
Why are you
up in my face?

82
00:08:59.758 --> 00:09:00.758
Pardon?

83
00:09:00.997 --> 00:09:02.457
Why do you...

84
00:09:02.898 --> 00:09:05.168
keep showing up
in front of me?

85
00:09:07.138 --> 00:09:09.038
Gosh, that Ji Soo Ho...

86
00:09:16.247 --> 00:09:17.548
Song Geu Rim?

87
00:09:18.107 --> 00:09:19.107
Yes.

88
00:09:19.508 --> 00:09:21.518
I think they're trying
to recruit Soo Ho...

89
00:09:21.577 --> 00:09:23.548
as their radio DJ.

90
00:09:23.918 --> 00:09:25.617
She would chase him around
during the shoot.

91
00:09:25.788 --> 00:09:27.188
He missed his shoot
for a commercial...

92
00:09:27.188 --> 00:09:28.188
because he drove her home.

93
00:09:28.188 --> 00:09:29.317
Get to the point.

94
00:09:31.087 --> 00:09:32.357
What does Soo Ho think?

95
00:09:33.457 --> 00:09:35.097
I'm not sure yet,

96
00:09:35.697 --> 00:09:36.997
but I think
he could be interested.

97
00:09:36.997 --> 00:09:39.538
Soo Ho doesn't have
a phone or a manager.

98
00:09:39.538 --> 00:09:41.567
That's why I asked you
to follow him around.

99
00:09:42.298 --> 00:09:44.808
However, you're always...

100
00:09:45.337 --> 00:09:47.278
disappointing me.

101
00:09:52.977 --> 00:09:54.418
(Jin Tae Ri)

102
00:09:56.388 --> 00:09:57.747
You're dismissed.

103
00:09:57.847 --> 00:09:58.847
Okay.

104
00:10:08.597 --> 00:10:09.768
Ms. Nam!

105
00:10:09.997 --> 00:10:12.597
Are there any updates
regarding the contract...

106
00:10:12.597 --> 00:10:14.538
with Ji Soo Ho
we talked about before?

107
00:10:15.038 --> 00:10:17.867
I'm with some reporters
right now,

108
00:10:17.867 --> 00:10:20.008
and I'm itching to talk.

109
00:10:22.278 --> 00:10:24.378
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

110
00:10:24.747 --> 00:10:25.947
What is this?

111
00:10:26.577 --> 00:10:27.817
Hey.

112
00:10:28.117 --> 00:10:31.947
I always had Ms. Choi
do my hair for years.

113
00:10:32.087 --> 00:10:35.357
Can someone
explain to me...

114
00:10:35.357 --> 00:10:36.888
why a rookie
is touching my hair?

115
00:10:37.087 --> 00:10:38.788
I'll do it properly.

116
00:10:40.857 --> 00:10:42.758
Stop touching my hair.

117
00:10:42.758 --> 00:10:45.567
I told you to get
Ms. Choi here.

118
00:10:45.567 --> 00:10:47.997
Yes, thank you.

119
00:10:50.438 --> 00:10:52.408
Gosh. Hello, Tae Ri.

120
00:10:57.247 --> 00:10:59.548
I've been watching
your 5pm drama.

121
00:11:11.558 --> 00:11:13.158
Hey!

122
00:11:16.158 --> 00:11:18.967
I'm your senior,
but you didn't say hello.

123
00:11:18.967 --> 00:11:21.168
I came out
to get your greeting.

124
00:11:23.668 --> 00:11:25.237
Do you have a problem
recognizing faces?

125
00:11:25.867 --> 00:11:29.178
Or maybe you never had
a television at home.

126
00:11:29.878 --> 00:11:32.707
Don't you know
how much earlier...

127
00:11:32.707 --> 00:11:35.048
I debuted before you...

128
00:11:35.048 --> 00:11:36.888
and appeared
on television?

129
00:11:38.117 --> 00:11:39.487
What is she talking about?

130
00:11:41.158 --> 00:11:43.388
Hey. Listen.

131
00:11:46.758 --> 00:11:50.097
Do you want to give me
a proper hello,

132
00:11:50.197 --> 00:11:53.737
or do you want to get
your hair ripped out...

133
00:11:53.737 --> 00:11:55.867
and get your name
in the headlines with me?

134
00:12:03.548 --> 00:12:04.808
Hey.

135
00:12:06.107 --> 00:12:08.648
If you don't
say hello again next time,

136
00:12:08.847 --> 00:12:11.888
I'll really
pull your hair out. Okay?

137
00:12:18.388 --> 00:12:19.597
Mr. Lee.

138
00:12:19.827 --> 00:12:21.628
Why did you ask me
to come here?

139
00:12:21.957 --> 00:12:23.128
What happened
to your foot?

140
00:12:26.398 --> 00:12:27.737
Well...

141
00:12:28.337 --> 00:12:30.408
Something happened.

142
00:12:30.967 --> 00:12:32.237
Mr. Lee...

143
00:12:32.237 --> 00:12:33.237
Come in.

144
00:12:49.518 --> 00:12:52.158
- This desk is for you.
- Pardon?

145
00:12:52.158 --> 00:12:54.457
Your desk is gone
because you got fired.

146
00:13:04.808 --> 00:13:07.577
I used to send in
a lot of postcards too.

147
00:13:11.247 --> 00:13:12.278
Isn't this place nice?

148
00:13:13.018 --> 00:13:14.018
Yes.

149
00:13:14.418 --> 00:13:16.247
It's nice, but...

150
00:13:16.247 --> 00:13:17.447
What about Ji Soo Ho?

151
00:13:19.758 --> 00:13:20.857
Well...

152
00:13:22.158 --> 00:13:24.258
I should talk to you
about him.

153
00:13:25.058 --> 00:13:27.658
Mr. Lee, I have something
to tell you.

154
00:13:31.367 --> 00:13:33.938
Let's talk outside.

155
00:13:37.867 --> 00:13:39.778
I met with Ji Soo Ho,

156
00:13:39.778 --> 00:13:42.278
and he's not a good fit
for radio.

157
00:13:42.278 --> 00:13:44.878
There are candidates
better than him.

158
00:13:44.878 --> 00:13:47.148
We don't even have
a concept yet.

159
00:13:47.148 --> 00:13:48.747
We can't cast a DJ...

160
00:13:48.747 --> 00:13:51.247
to find out later
he doesn't fit our theme.

161
00:13:51.247 --> 00:13:53.487
Are you saying he said no?

162
00:13:53.487 --> 00:13:56.188
No,
that's not what I mean.

163
00:13:57.658 --> 00:13:58.727
How is Oh Ji Soo?

164
00:13:58.727 --> 00:14:00.457
She's really hot
these days.

165
00:14:00.457 --> 00:14:01.597
So he won't do it?

166
00:14:01.597 --> 00:14:03.367
I mean...

167
00:14:03.867 --> 00:14:06.567
Why does it have to be
Ji Soo Ho?

168
00:14:07.038 --> 00:14:10.867
I was trying
not to go this far,

169
00:14:11.438 --> 00:14:15.477
but Ji Soo Ho
is completely crazy.

170
00:14:19.508 --> 00:14:22.747
That's okay.
I'm more crazy.

171
00:14:25.148 --> 00:14:26.148
But...

172
00:14:28.457 --> 00:14:29.457
Ji Soo Ho...

173
00:14:30.288 --> 00:14:32.357
doesn't look like
a radio person, does he?

174
00:14:32.727 --> 00:14:34.827
I think he would
totally look down on us.

175
00:14:35.128 --> 00:14:37.268
How did you know?

176
00:14:37.398 --> 00:14:38.428
Geu Rim.

177
00:14:39.638 --> 00:14:41.697
He's the most unlikely
person...

178
00:14:41.697 --> 00:14:44.138
to become friendly
with radio.

179
00:14:45.337 --> 00:14:48.178
Isn't that something
we should make happen?

180
00:14:50.347 --> 00:14:51.947
I have one more reason,

181
00:14:53.648 --> 00:14:55.317
but I'll tell you
once you recruit him.

182
00:14:57.648 --> 00:14:59.487
Are you serious?

183
00:15:02.388 --> 00:15:04.288
What do I do?

184
00:15:23.077 --> 00:15:26.817
(Dear Moon Sung Woo...)

185
00:15:30.587 --> 00:15:32.347
If you're fired, go away.

186
00:15:33.117 --> 00:15:36.327
Come on,
don't be like that.

187
00:15:36.727 --> 00:15:38.487
Why are you playing
hard to get?

188
00:15:39.028 --> 00:15:42.197
What are you so dying
to talk to me about?

189
00:15:42.658 --> 00:15:45.597
You have been a DJ
for 30 years.

190
00:15:45.928 --> 00:15:47.837
You persuaded listeners
all over the world.

191
00:15:47.837 --> 00:15:51.067
You're a radio star
who lasted for so long.

192
00:15:51.737 --> 00:15:54.038
That's why
you should tell me.

193
00:15:54.077 --> 00:15:55.278
Tell you what?

194
00:15:55.508 --> 00:15:58.308
How to persuade someone
that hates radios.

195
00:15:58.477 --> 00:16:02.247
You made me into a writer.
You can't ignore me now.

196
00:16:03.987 --> 00:16:05.388
Don't blame it on me.

197
00:16:05.418 --> 00:16:06.788
It's true.

198
00:16:07.587 --> 00:16:11.028
My mom and I have been
your fans for 10 years.

199
00:16:11.128 --> 00:16:12.827
Look. I probably sent...

200
00:16:12.827 --> 00:16:15.357
over 100 postcards
to your show.

201
00:16:15.697 --> 00:16:18.727
I learned Korean and music
through your show.

202
00:16:18.727 --> 00:16:21.197
I even learned life
and writing.

203
00:16:21.737 --> 00:16:24.567
Then why are you
so bad at writing?

204
00:16:27.438 --> 00:16:29.408
What is it
that you want me to do?

205
00:16:29.977 --> 00:16:33.477
How can I help you
recruit Ji Soo Ho?

206
00:16:34.617 --> 00:16:37.847
Mom and I got through
hard times thanks to you.

207
00:16:38.317 --> 00:16:40.217
Just like
how you convinced me,

208
00:16:40.217 --> 00:16:43.258
tell me how I can
convince Ji Soo Ho...

209
00:16:43.428 --> 00:16:46.658
I was convinced by radio
not because...

210
00:16:47.128 --> 00:16:49.528
of a strategy
but due to sincerity.

211
00:16:52.898 --> 00:16:54.967
I'll get going.

212
00:16:55.168 --> 00:16:57.737
Thank you. I love you.

213
00:17:03.107 --> 00:17:04.947
Do you still not want
a phone?

214
00:17:05.747 --> 00:17:06.817
If you don't want
a manager,

215
00:17:06.817 --> 00:17:07.847
how about a secretary?

216
00:17:08.577 --> 00:17:10.618
It wouldn't be
my secretary but yours.

217
00:17:11.118 --> 00:17:12.247
Whichever.

218
00:17:12.648 --> 00:17:13.717
I don't need one.

219
00:17:14.757 --> 00:17:16.828
Then
should I fire Mr. Kim too?

220
00:17:18.057 --> 00:17:20.598
I hired him
because you wanted him.

221
00:17:20.858 --> 00:17:23.997
However, you are turning
Mr. Kim into a scarecrow.

222
00:17:27.967 --> 00:17:30.267
We'll talk about
business now.

223
00:17:31.267 --> 00:17:33.078
(Documentary film
production proposal)

224
00:17:34.977 --> 00:17:38.378
They want to shoot a film
about our family.

225
00:17:39.007 --> 00:17:40.947
The director
is Kim Sang Soo.

226
00:17:41.017 --> 00:17:44.688
We will handle all product
placement and marketing.

227
00:17:46.588 --> 00:17:49.828
I thought we did enough.
Must we sell ourselves?

228
00:17:50.588 --> 00:17:51.658
Of course.

229
00:17:52.658 --> 00:17:55.398
Just walking and breathing
can get you money.

230
00:17:56.057 --> 00:17:58.997
You must know how much
it would be in a year.

231
00:18:00.168 --> 00:18:01.237
I won't do it.

232
00:18:03.438 --> 00:18:05.908
You missed a schedule
last night.

233
00:18:06.707 --> 00:18:10.447
It cost a lot to stop
articles ruining our name.

234
00:18:12.207 --> 00:18:14.477
I didn't want
to bring this up.

235
00:18:24.088 --> 00:18:25.787
It's your birthday
next month.

236
00:18:26.457 --> 00:18:28.158
I'm giving you an early
birthday present...

237
00:18:28.158 --> 00:18:29.668
since it's getting cold.

238
00:18:40.138 --> 00:18:41.277
Son.

239
00:18:43.007 --> 00:18:45.108
Didn't I tell you?

240
00:18:46.517 --> 00:18:49.247
What you're good at,
what you're bad at,

241
00:18:49.247 --> 00:18:50.547
and what you just do...

242
00:18:51.188 --> 00:18:52.787
Even breathing...

243
00:18:53.418 --> 00:18:55.487
could harm me.

244
00:18:59.658 --> 00:19:01.557
I'll set the meeting with
the director next week.

245
00:19:02.297 --> 00:19:04.668
We'll follow our script
as always.

246
00:19:10.368 --> 00:19:11.608
I won't do it.

247
00:19:12.138 --> 00:19:14.578
I don't think I can smile
in front of the cameras...

248
00:19:16.207 --> 00:19:17.608
running around me
for 24 hours.

249
00:19:29.517 --> 00:19:31.858
Your dad went to a shoot
overseas.

250
00:19:31.858 --> 00:19:33.858
We'll have a party
on our own.

251
00:19:33.997 --> 00:19:35.098
Okay.

252
00:19:35.858 --> 00:19:38.898
The candles are dripping.
Hurry and blow them out.

253
00:19:47.537 --> 00:19:48.537
Happy birthday.

254
00:19:58.088 --> 00:19:59.188
Soo Ho.

255
00:20:01.588 --> 00:20:03.987
I have something to say
for your birthday.

256
00:20:11.297 --> 00:20:12.527
You are not...

257
00:20:13.338 --> 00:20:14.767
my son.

258
00:20:19.408 --> 00:20:23.047
So, what you're good at,

259
00:20:23.047 --> 00:20:25.777
what you're bad at,
what you just do,

260
00:20:25.947 --> 00:20:27.578
and even your breathing...

261
00:20:28.777 --> 00:20:30.747
Make sure none of it
bothers me.

262
00:20:31.787 --> 00:20:33.787
You have to do a good job,
okay?

263
00:21:11.257 --> 00:21:12.287
Doc.

264
00:21:17.098 --> 00:21:18.128
Hey, Doc.

265
00:21:18.628 --> 00:21:20.568
- Yes, Patient?
- Give me sleeping pills.

266
00:21:20.868 --> 00:21:21.868
Declined.

267
00:21:21.868 --> 00:21:24.438
If you get consultation,
I will prescribe you.

