799
00:55:07.597 --> 00:55:09.097
Hello, Soo Ho.

800
00:55:09.927 --> 00:55:12.898
I am Song Geu Rim,
a radio writer...

801
00:55:12.898 --> 00:55:15.037
who wants to write
the warmest words ever.

802
00:55:15.867 --> 00:55:19.338
I've prepared this video
to introduce to you,

803
00:55:19.577 --> 00:55:22.407
the radio, which I love...

804
00:55:22.407 --> 00:55:24.048
so very much.

805
00:55:25.608 --> 00:55:28.577
The postcards I sent in
when I was in...

806
00:55:28.577 --> 00:55:31.418
middle school and high
school are still up.

807
00:55:32.287 --> 00:55:35.758
I loved the radio and
listened every day.

808
00:55:37.588 --> 00:55:41.528
This booth belongs to
KBC Radio's legend,

809
00:55:41.528 --> 00:55:43.898
a DJ of 30 years.

810
00:55:47.168 --> 00:55:49.097
Yes. This is the office...

811
00:55:49.168 --> 00:55:51.508
where I write my scripts.

812
00:55:52.137 --> 00:55:54.707
It may look like
a storage room,

813
00:55:54.807 --> 00:55:56.448
but it is my writing room.

814
00:55:57.548 --> 00:55:59.747
And here.

815
00:56:00.218 --> 00:56:02.847
Do you see all the
scripts that I hope...

816
00:56:02.847 --> 00:56:04.148
you'd read?

817
00:56:04.287 --> 00:56:05.648
Will you please save them?

818
00:56:08.588 --> 00:56:11.657
This is the place
I love the most.

819
00:56:12.028 --> 00:56:14.028
My hideout.

820
00:56:18.898 --> 00:56:20.097
Soo Ho.

821
00:56:20.537 --> 00:56:22.798
I'm not a good writer,

822
00:56:23.168 --> 00:56:26.307
and I can't do anything
well right now.

823
00:56:27.238 --> 00:56:30.608
But if you say you'd do
the radio show with me,

824
00:56:30.977 --> 00:56:32.878
and the words
that I write...

825
00:56:33.077 --> 00:56:36.787
are read to the world
with your voice,

826
00:56:37.218 --> 00:56:40.057
I may bow down to you
that very day.

827
00:56:42.057 --> 00:56:43.528
Does that sound like
a threat?

828
00:56:44.528 --> 00:56:45.727
Anyway,

829
00:56:46.427 --> 00:56:48.698
I hope you will...

830
00:56:48.698 --> 00:56:51.727
knock on this door.

831
00:56:53.068 --> 00:56:55.168
Let's do the radio show
together.

832
00:58:28.528 --> 00:58:29.927
Hello, Mr. Kang.

833
00:58:30.028 --> 00:58:31.827
Get up here
right this instant.

834
00:58:45.247 --> 00:58:47.677
Song Geu Rim will be
your main writer?

835
00:58:48.577 --> 00:58:51.017
Hey, Crazy Gang.
Have you lost your mind?

836
00:58:52.918 --> 00:58:55.188
Song Geu Rim
is a problem too.

837
00:58:55.218 --> 00:58:57.387
Did she say she'll do it?

838
00:58:57.488 --> 00:59:00.457
Did she agree, saying
she'll be the main writer?

839
00:59:01.258 --> 00:59:03.528
Okay. Fine.

840
00:59:03.528 --> 00:59:06.938
You're working together
to drive me crazy, right?

841
00:59:08.097 --> 00:59:10.338
Geu Rim. Get over here.

842
00:59:11.807 --> 00:59:14.938
Are you really going to be
the main writer...

843
00:59:15.378 --> 00:59:17.008
as it says
in the proposal?

844
00:59:17.778 --> 00:59:20.747
Mr. Kang. You agreed that
I can staff...

845
00:59:20.747 --> 00:59:22.988
Crazy Gang. Don't talk.

846
00:59:24.117 --> 00:59:27.657
I'm trying to save
this radio station...

847
00:59:27.918 --> 00:59:30.887
and begged until my hands
bled to save you.

848
00:59:30.927 --> 00:59:34.057
Are you trying to say
we should die together?

849
00:59:34.997 --> 00:59:38.597
How could you
make her the main writer?

850
00:59:39.227 --> 00:59:42.267
She can't write
a single script properly.

851
00:59:42.267 --> 00:59:43.438
- What...
- Mr. Kang.

852
00:59:43.438 --> 00:59:46.307
You.
Don't say another word.

853
00:59:47.537 --> 00:59:48.778
You talk.

854
00:59:49.747 --> 00:59:52.577
Can you really be
the main writer?

855
00:59:54.247 --> 00:59:57.188
It says right here,
"Main writer,"

856
00:59:57.188 --> 00:59:59.048
"Song Geu Rim."

857
00:59:59.287 --> 01:00:02.758
Can you create a show
and write the script well?

858
01:00:03.157 --> 01:00:04.258
Can you?

859
01:00:08.957 --> 01:00:10.298
You now Ms. La, right?

860
01:00:12.798 --> 01:00:14.438
Work with her.

861
01:00:14.968 --> 01:00:18.108
If you really want to work
with Geu Rim,

862
01:00:18.267 --> 01:00:21.037
you can use her
as an assistant writer.

863
01:00:21.608 --> 01:00:23.747
Ms. La. Is that okay?

864
01:00:26.247 --> 01:00:27.948
She said, "Okay."

865
01:00:30.747 --> 01:00:32.347
I'll work with Geu Rim.

866
01:00:37.957 --> 01:00:39.927
Fine.

867
01:00:41.858 --> 01:00:44.367
As it says
in this proposal,

868
01:00:44.597 --> 01:00:46.597
if Ji Soo Ho agrees
to do it,

869
01:00:47.398 --> 01:00:49.707
you can be the main
writer. You have...

870
01:00:50.438 --> 01:00:51.707
my seal of approval.

871
01:00:52.008 --> 01:00:54.878
So? Did he agree to do it?

872
01:00:55.508 --> 01:00:58.948
Did you even get him
to agree?

873
01:00:59.407 --> 01:01:00.747
No, right?

874
01:01:00.847 --> 01:01:02.718
He refuses, right?

875
01:01:02.718 --> 01:01:06.517
Even without Ji Soo Ho,
I'm working with Geu Rim.

876
01:01:10.488 --> 01:01:12.787
Hey, Crazy Gang.
Where are you going?

877
01:01:13.497 --> 01:01:15.657
Forget coming back
to work!

878
01:01:15.657 --> 01:01:17.867
Forget the whole thing,
you punk!

879
01:01:18.568 --> 01:01:21.497
Sorry, Ms. La.
He'll change his mind.

880
01:01:21.968 --> 01:01:23.267
- It's okay.
- Be understanding.

881
01:01:35.948 --> 01:01:37.188
Geu Rim.

882
01:01:43.688 --> 01:01:45.157
Did you really think...

883
01:01:48.497 --> 01:01:50.497
if you got Ji Soo Ho
to join,

884
01:01:51.267 --> 01:01:53.637
you could be
the main writer?

885
01:01:56.307 --> 01:01:59.508
Wake up, will you,
Geu Rim?

886
01:02:00.207 --> 01:02:02.477
Even if you're good at
winning over guests...

887
01:02:02.477 --> 01:02:05.148
and at kissing up
to people,

888
01:02:06.077 --> 01:02:08.718
if you can't write,
you'll go on air...

889
01:02:08.718 --> 01:02:10.688
and humiliate yourself.

890
01:02:11.387 --> 01:02:14.088
You know your limitations,
don't you?

891
01:02:18.528 --> 01:02:20.858
I don't know how you got
Lee Gang to pick you...

892
01:02:20.858 --> 01:02:22.157
to be the main writer,

893
01:02:22.427 --> 01:02:25.097
but Ji Soo Ho...

894
01:02:25.698 --> 01:02:28.338
Do you really think
that's even possible?

895
01:02:29.838 --> 01:02:32.938
Is that why you're here?
You think it can happen?

896
01:02:33.378 --> 01:02:36.807
Like Ji Soo Ho would
really DJ a radio show.

897
01:02:37.648 --> 01:02:40.218
Geu Rim.
I'm saying this...

898
01:02:40.247 --> 01:02:42.948
because I'm concerned
for you. I mean it.

899
01:02:43.117 --> 01:02:45.048
Wake up
and smell the coffee!

900
01:02:45.188 --> 01:02:48.157
The probability of him
becoming a radio DJ...

901
01:02:48.157 --> 01:02:49.488
is much worse than you
becoming a main writer.

902
01:02:50.427 --> 01:02:51.457
Got that?

903
01:02:52.997 --> 01:02:54.597
I'll do the radio show.

904
01:02:57.497 --> 01:02:59.668
Let's do the radio show.

905
01:03:42.838 --> 01:03:44.307
(Radio Romance)

906
01:03:44.677 --> 01:03:45.807
Want to be my AD?

907
01:03:46.378 --> 01:03:47.778
Work with me.

908
01:03:47.948 --> 01:03:50.048
You really agreed?
Because of Lady Kamikaze?

909
01:03:50.048 --> 01:03:51.218
It wasn't
because of her.

910
01:03:51.218 --> 01:03:53.258
He wants to choose
the guests and his lines?

911
01:03:53.258 --> 01:03:54.418
How did you know?

912
01:03:54.418 --> 01:03:56.088
I heard we're battling.

913
01:03:56.088 --> 01:03:57.688
This is absurd.
A battle?

914
01:03:57.827 --> 01:04:00.997
I'll sign the contract
only with Song Geu Rim.

915
01:04:01.298 --> 01:04:02.497
Let me ask one thing.

916
01:04:02.497 --> 01:04:04.367
That's the best thing
I've heard. Ask 100.

917
01:04:04.767 --> 01:04:06.537
Why did I agree
to go on the radio?

918
01:04:06.597 --> 01:04:08.738
Will you not do it then?

